{{ 'template-rewards.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}

<section class="swell-faq">
	<h2>Ready to Join</h2>
	<ul class="swell-faq-list">
        <li>
        </li>
      
		<li>
			<span class="swell-faq-text">How do I join Monday Rewards?</span><span class="swell-faq-load-more">+</span>
			<p class="swell-faq-explanation">It’s easy - simply sign up here. After that, every order you place will go towards your Reward status. Your tier will upgrade automatically once you reach those lifetime spends.</p>
		</li>

		<li>
			<span class="swell-faq-text">What do I get for joining?</span><span class="swell-faq-load-more">+</span>
			<p class="swell-faq-explanation">All members will receive an annual gift from us on their birthday. As you shop more, you’ll earn more rewards.</p>
		</li>
      
      
        <li>
			<span class="swell-faq-text">What does “lifetime spend” mean?</span><span class="swell-faq-load-more">+</span>
			<p class="swell-faq-explanation">Your lifetime spend is the total amount of money you’ve spent with Monday, excluding any discounts or refunds. After you unlock a new tier, all you have to do to maintain your status is to spend $50 in the following 12 months.</p>
		</li>
      
      
        <li>
			<span class="swell-faq-text">What’s the birthday gift?</span><span class="swell-faq-load-more">+</span>
			<p class="swell-faq-explanation">Like all the best gifts, this one is a surprise. But here’s a little hint: it could be a discount, a freebie, or something just for you.</p>
		</li>
      
      
        <li>
			<span class="swell-faq-text">Can I use all my referral credits at once?</span><span class="swell-faq-load-more">+</span>
			<p class="swell-faq-explanation">Yes! You can use your credits however you like. Spend them all at once or spread them out over a few purchases. You’ll have the option when checking out.</p>
		</li>
      
      
        <li>
			<span class="swell-faq-text">How do I get my benefits?</span><span class="swell-faq-load-more">+</span>
			<p class="swell-faq-explanation">All you have to do is shop! Any rewards or benefits will be automatically applied to your account.</p>
		</li>
      
        <li>
			<span class="swell-faq-text">Will my past purchases count towards my Monday Rewards?</span><span class="swell-faq-load-more">+</span>
			<p class="swell-faq-explanation">The last 12 months of spend from 4/21/2019 will count towards your tier status.</p>
		</li>


      <li>
			<span class="swell-faq-text">Does my rewards discount make my order final sale?</span><span class="swell-faq-load-more">+</span>
			<p class="swell-faq-explanation">No, the rewards discount that is automatically applied to each order does not make your purchase final sale.</p>
		</li>
      
	</ul>
</section>

{% comment %} <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.2.1/jquery.min.js"></script> {% endcomment %}

<script>
window.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", ()=>{
  $('.swell-faq-list li').click(function(e){
    e.preventDefault();
    $(this).find('.swell-faq-explanation').toggleClass('swell-faq-show swell-faq-hide');
    
  
  if($(this).find('.swell-faq-explanation').css('display')=="none"){
    $(this).find('.swell-faq-load-more').text('+');
  }
  else{
    $(this).find('.swell-faq-load-more').text('-');
  }
  
});
})
  
  
</script>


<style>
  
  .swell-faq {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    width: 100%;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    padding-top: 5rem;
    background: #F2F0E8;
}

.swell-faq h2 {
    width: 100%;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
}

.swell-faq h2:after {
    content: "Want discounts, gifts, and exclusive early access? All you have to do is shop.";
    display: block;
    padding-top: 10px;
    font-family: 'ABC Favorit', sans-serif;
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    letter-spacing: .02em;
}

.swell-faq-list {
    width: 80%;
    padding-bottom: 60px;
}

.swell-faq-explanation {
    text-align: left;
    display: none;
    width: 100%;
}

.swell-faq-text {
    font-weight: 200;
}

.swell-faq-load-more {
    font-weight: 200;
    font-size: 16px;
}

.swell-faq-list li {
    list-style: none;
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
